{"tid":1309462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正撚量] 到底有冇暴動呀屌？","createTime":"2019-07-12T08:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T15:13:51.000Z","uid":168703,"like":57,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7d08ace5ee6e2d301fc4f91fb87f8de6d34aa725","tid":1309462,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qhNfgqf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqhNfgqf.png&h=a8e7bef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來班毅進仔唔知數學差，理解能力都出現問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>見身邊嘅人呢排都因為成個香港嘅環境感到好壓抑，想大家心情舒緩返啲，同時又唔想大家鬆懈落黎，無咩叻淨係識鳩up，想試下用一個輕鬆啲嘅方式去講下政治野。你有一秒覺得好笑我都覺得自己成功左架啦，好笑嘅比個正評或者遞比身邊個人睇下，將呢份笑容傳開去。</em>"},{"pid":"e8fb4a2fe01d1755e582968f186044df69ad951f","tid":1309462,"uid":168703,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:14:47.000Z","msg":"除此之外，同朋友傾過想開埋個ig分享下呢啲訊息，始終有啲人真係懶到連懶人包都唔會睇，希望呢啲輕鬆啲好笑啲嘅post可以帶佢地了解下政治情況，如果可以嘅大家follow埋呢個ig同share比多啲人呀！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/positivelunface?igshid=10f52mz5bkc08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fpositivelunface%3Figshid%3D10f52mz5bkc08&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=1076cac6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/positivelunface?igshid=10f52mz5bkc08</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>另外都仲有個post架可以睇埋呀！</em><br />\n<br />\n<em>[正撚量] 今日想同大家簡單咁討論下評分系統</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307610</a><br />\n<em>- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</em>"},{"pid":"b2ca3516178b7cc996f4053c94500de219c0b894","tid":1309462,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcd11639aeac7a0509259ef0f940464724d68ec","tid":13